deal_text: appreciated...review by - yelp michael r.: i love finding good wings in the area and lucky's definitely has some great ones. i got the sweet to heat but my favorite so far were the honey mustard. they also allow you to order all flats or drums if you prefer. there was disney trivia the night we went and it was overall a great time.review by - yelp jennifer s.:
